{"tid":2072361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男人控制著冷氣開關是氣候變化的主因","createTime":"2020-06-20T13:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T06:47:11.000Z","uid":169112,"like":56,"dislike":301,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"ae865558ede1058f0f1f6c4062e3b44366d986a7","tid":2072361,"uid":169112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"【無處不在的父權】<br />\n<br />\n今年的五月是香港有記錄以來最熱的，在眾人大呼「熱熱熱」的時候，香港政確會告訴你氣候的真正原因和其政確的解決之道。<br />\n<br />\n很多人都知道碳排放是全球氣溫急升的原因，但卻很少人知道碳排與性別不公，亦即父權制度的密切關係。根據調查，男人比女人的碳排放多70%，男人也比女人更不關心氣溫暖化和不認為自己對氣候變化有責任。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，女人卻承受著氣溫變化的惡果！研果顯示女人在天災（氣溫變化而急增）中死去的機會比男人大得多；而由此很多女人是農民，氣溫變化也令她們的生活百上加斤。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，氣溫變化不過是全球性性別不公的延伸。<br />\n<br />\n既然氣溫變化不過是性別權力的不平等，那麼真正的解決之道只可能是全面落實性別正義和讓權力從男性專制中解放出來。<br />\n<br />\n我們必須認清，性別不公是全面且無孔不入的，父權制度可謂無處不在。簡單如家居中的冷氣遙控的控制權，就往往被男人所專權控制。而這微權力操作的集合，就是造成今日氣溫變化的惡果。<br />\n<br />\n而且有關氣溫變化的知識產制亦是高度男性化的結果，這點Nancy Tuana已清楚指出。這種知識限制和規訓了我們的想像。<br />\n<br />\n因此冷氣遙控必須從家中的男人手上解放出來，否則氣候問題只會無日無之。隨著氣候問題日益嚴重，全球女性向父權作全面抗爭已是刻不容緩，這抗爭同時是要拯救男性。因為氣溫問題惡化下去，男人亦不能獨善其身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8CYPjmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8CYPjmL.jpg&h=01c18b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n【Are women the key to solving CLIMATE CHANGE? Females produce less pollution than men when travelling, study reveals】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3159604/Are-women-key-solving-CLIMATE-CHANGE-Females-produce-pollution-men-travelling-study-reveals.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsciencetech%2Farticle-3159604%2FAre-women-key-solving-CLIMATE-CHANGE-Females-produce-pollution-men-travelling-study-reveals.html&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdufSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=d736ef9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-3159604/Are-women-key-solving-CLIMATE-CHANGE-Females-produce-pollution-men-travelling-study-reveals.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【Gendering Climate Knowledge for Justice: Catalyzing a New Research Agenda】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-94-007-5518-5_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1007%2F978-94-007-5518-5_2&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdufSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=58e9ecb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-94-007-5518-5_2</a><br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Climate_change_and_gender#Mitigation_and_adaptation_efforts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FClimate_change_and_gender%23Mitigation_and_adaptation_efforts&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdufSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=987ecba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Climate_change_and_gender#Mitigation_and_adaptation_efforts</a><br />\n<br />\n原Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/1727459814010844/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCorrectness%2Fphotos%2Fa.1282790118477818%2F1727459814010844%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdufSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c8bc47bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCorrectness/photos/a.1282790118477818/1727459814010844/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"74ff1aa0f7aeabe641c6a9b679e2c0cb2ab117b8","tid":2072361,"uid":155818,"like":364,"dislike":1,"score":363,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"母權就真<br />\n開冷氣都要問過老母<br />\n開幾多度都要佢訂<br />\n父你老母權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712e1bcea6528d71e2757d0b7a19629e5ac09ed","tid":2072361,"uid":242102,"like":58,"dislike":4,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:58:55.000Z","msg":"你講得啱，<br />\n當初男人發明嘅冷氣就係惡因惡果"},{"pid":"49fb8cba365f77ed2cc1c1a435efc8aa1a90fe59","tid":2072361,"uid":169112,"like":2,"disl